      usr/share/gnome/apps/Multimedia.
  * debian/patches/00list:
    + 20_no-wx-updates.dpatch: disabled the update check.
    + 20_interfaces.dpatch: disabled deprecated patch.
  * configure.ac:
    + Fixes powerpc build.
